Package: libcassandra-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcassandra0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Cassandra Thrift C++ Binding (Developement Libraries and Headers)
 Contains the symlinks, headers, and object files needed to compile
 and link programs which use the cassandra C++ library that generated by
 Thrift compiler.

Package: libcassandra0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cassandra Thrift C++ Binding
 This package provides a library providing an API to communicate
 with Cassandra Database. The source was generated from cassandra.thrift
 by Thrift compiler.
